These are my config files.

If you have any questions about settings email me at alexseubert@gmail.com.

These will be in a state of flux perpetually and I may or may not recall what I
was intending to do with any given setting.

Special tmux comment: I have set up separate tmux config files to allow for the
use of tmux-MacOSX-pasteboard and use a shell script locally on OS X to force
the use of the OSX config.  See
https://github.com/ChrisJohnsen/tmux-MacOSX-pasteboard/issues/8 for details.
